rows.label: tlk41200122_03_msg0001
rows.name:
It's time to feed the Armu! It's
a properly balanced meal, too!

rows.label: tlk41200122_03_msg0002
rows.name:
Just because Armu are herbivores
doesn't mean they only eat
pasture grass, you know?

rows.label: tlk41200122_03_msg0003
rows.name:
You have to give them Ruby Mangosteens
to strengthen their teeth, and Deadly
Kiwis to keep their vitamins in balance!

rows.label: tlk41200122_03_msg0004
rows.name: Think it's a lot of work?

rows.label: tlk41200122_03_msg0005
rows.name:
But for my cute little Armu,
it's no trouble at all.
